{"tid":2398028,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"中年漢Donki偷底褲牛肉斷正　醒目店員發現截停報警","createTime":"2021-02-07T03:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T05:12:16.000Z","uid":81228,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b752cb637493e349941e9b0a5eda2528b7cd59e9","tid":2398028,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:01:01.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴彌敦道Donki（驚安之殿堂）發生偷竊案。今（7日）清晨約5時，一名55歲姓馮男子疑趁商店準備關門期間，將貨物放進膠袋中，企圖在店員疏於防範時離開店鋪。惟店內一名男店員發現該男子形跡可疑，於他離開店鋪時上前截停，並於袋中發現未有付款的貨物，立即報警處理。警員接報到場，在他袋內發現底褲、牛肉及零食等貨物，價值約900元，以涉嫌偷竊將他拘捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210207/434966628166275072625047.jpeg/no8Dcp0tQJpoiaO1IwM-VnTUoXF2rT243Wrgyehq4Mk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210207%2F434966628166275072625047.jpeg%2Fno8Dcp0tQJpoiaO1IwM-VnTUoXF2rT243Wrgyehq4Mk%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2346edd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子疑在店鋪內偷去貨物，被警店帶走調查。（陳永武攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210207/434966714707349504048791.jpeg/MU3UE18X6EYtxA6M409R5pbVh1TZ2_5KVQPTF2AD0xc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210207%2F434966714707349504048791.jpeg%2FMU3UE18X6EYtxA6M409R5pbVh1TZ2_5KVQPTF2AD0xc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d2ed5eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子疑在店鋪內偷去貨物，被警店帶走調查。（陳永武攝）[/img]<br />\n<br />\n撰文：張家豪　陳永武"},{"pid":"c2e81db18d87e9f3845d1d1fe42d774a2e76446c","tid":2398028,"uid":151534,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"藍=放<br />\n黃=拉"},{"pid":"861164cdff7ed9b0c77c321c8acac7833e9d657d","tid":2398028,"uid":123848,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"似休班狗"},{"pid":"c7ec4937509fef18f173a07f7ba44a2de59a91f0","tid":2398028,"uid":260587,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"識偷一定偷半價中拖羅"},{"pid":"2dc0f6ac65a1b68dbf8f707bf2d38255a1e3833e